ON

TLS, 2 pp. Glenn Horowitz.





Zermatt, July 24, 1962

Hotel Mt. Cervin

Dear Joan and Peter,

We feel terrible to find that Joan's letter of many weeks ago was not answered sooner. We had hoped for a while that the LOLITA premiere might take place in London, but no, it was New York, and Vladimir naturally wanted to attend. We sailed on the Queen Elizabeth on May 31 and came back on its next trip. This allowed us exactly two very busy, very amusing, very tiring weeks in New York plus exactl